data.body:
- VSCode Version:1.1.0-insider
- OS Version: 10.0.10586

Steps to Reproduce:
1. In my DbContext derived class, I replaced,
   `public virtual DbSet<NewsItem> NewsItem { get; set; }` by
   `public virtual DbSet<NewsItem> NewsItems { get; set; }` 
2. In HomeController.cs I replaced

```
        public IActionResult Index()
        {
            return View(_db.NewsItem);
        }
```

by

```
        public IActionResult Index()
        {
            return View(_db.NewsItems);
        }
```

3  Save all files and click debug to build and run. The following error is detected during preLaunchTask 'build'

'xxxxxContext' does not contain a definition for 'NewsItems' and no extension method .......

4  Close down and reopen project
5  Click debug and application builds and runs ok. Error??? is no longer detected by vscode
